Rating: 4
This was a big hit at our Thanksgiving dinner and got rave reviews from 18 people. The apricots added a surprise flavor to the the sweet potatoes that gave them a very unique taste. It was almost like eating dessert. Also, the fact that it is pureed is a bit different and gave it a very fine, light, almost baby food texture. Definitely give these a try some time...they'll make you smile!

